        <h2 class="section-heading">Who are we?</h2>
        <p class="lead">Eat with Catalans is a nonprofit initiative purely driven by our hospitality and our will to explain our culture and our Republic to the world.
        </br>
        The promoters and supporters of Eat with Catalans have three things in common:
          <ol class="lead">
            <li> We enjoy eating local food </li>
            <li> We like to socialize </li>
            <li> We like to explain the Catalan culture, traditions and why we build a modern and inclusive Republic to people from abroad </li>
          </ol>
          <p class="lead">
